  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"i-DTXDx7\">首先你要给出性别的定义，是专指人类还是包括所有动物。</p><p data-pid=\"FYeG757G\">其次要说明是客观生理机体，还是主观自我认定。</p><p data-pid=\"T5CIuUsj\">第三，就算是人类生理层面上，还要分析一下，是基因层面，染色体层面，还是性器官<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=334660136&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%BE%81&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">第二性征<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>层面。</p><p data-pid=\"_8omyzD8\">第四，考虑一下病变与连续性问题。</p><p data-pid=\"MonPbAnX\">西方的LGBTQIA的说法就分属三类。LGB是性取向，TI是生理性别相关，QA则是主观认定。反正乱成一团。至于所谓五十六种性别本质是基于两性性别的自我感觉，比<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=334660136&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B0%91%E7%A7%91&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">民科<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>还恶心的东西。米国搞<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=334660136&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">身份政治<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的产物。</p><p data-pid=\"Et--xCL0\">本想在个人专栏写作，被和谐，关了七天。心累。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
